    <item>
      <title>BMO 通过与另类资产管理公司达成协议扩大私人信贷业务范围</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-10/bmo-expands-private-credit-reach-via-deal-with-alternative-asset-manager</link>
      <description><![CDATA[蒙特利尔银行金融集团 (BMO Financial Group) 已与另类资产管理公司 Canal Road Group 达成合作伙伴关系，该协议将使后者能够投资高达 10 亿美元的直接贷款，因为这家加拿大银行正寻求扩大其在蓬勃发展的私人信贷市场的份额。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-10/bmo-expands-private-credit-reach-via-deal-with-alternative-asset-manager</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 10 Jan 2025 21:34:54 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>2024 年是“疯狂叙事之年”：Axonic 的 Cecchini</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2025-01-10/2024-a-year-of-manic-narratives-axonic-s-cecchini-video</link>
      <description><![CDATA[Axonic Capital 负责人 Peter Cecchini 表示，2024 年对美联储和市场来说是“疯狂叙事的一年”，并表示美联储“过早停止了战斗”。贝莱德宏观信贷研究主管 Amanda Lynam 喜欢浮动利率敞口，并认为它“对投资者来说非常有吸引力”。他们与 Vonnie Quinn 就“实际收益率”进行了交谈。（来源：彭博社）]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2025-01-10/2024-a-year-of-manic-narratives-axonic-s-cecchini-video</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 10 Jan 2025 21:02:40 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>富国银行认为，如果收益率超过 5%，股票将面临风险</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2025-01-10/wells-fargo-sees-risk-for-stocks-if-yields-go-beyond-5-video</link>
      <description><![CDATA[富国银行投资研究所全球资产配置策略主管 Tracie McMillion 表示，她预计股市将在 2025 年走高，市场波动性的增加将为投资者带来机会。McMillion 在“Bloomberg The Close”节目中解释了她如何看待这些机会。（来源：彭博社）]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2025-01-10/wells-fargo-sees-risk-for-stocks-if-yields-go-beyond-5-video</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 10 Jan 2025 20:47:05 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>就业报告激增 华尔街担忧“双输”市场</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-10/blowout-jobs-report-fuels-wall-street-fear-of-lose-lose-market</link>
      <description><![CDATA[事情不应该是这样的。随着经济蓬勃发展，友好的美联储为其提供支持，唐纳德·特朗普入主白宫，随着日历翻阅，华尔街只看到了上涨的迹象。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-10/blowout-jobs-report-fuels-wall-street-fear-of-lose-lose-market</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 10 Jan 2025 19:05:09 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>意外招聘激增推高收益率，美元上涨</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-10/aussie-dollar-lowest-since-2020-as-greenback-surges-on-us-data</link>
      <description><![CDATA[就业报告好于预期，增强了人们对美联储将在今年下半年之前推迟再次降息的猜测，美元因此飙升。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-10/aussie-dollar-lowest-since-2020-as-greenback-surges-on-us-data</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 10 Jan 2025 14:14:51 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>交易员推迟美联储降息，美国国债收益率测试 5%</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-10/treasuries-tumble-as-traders-push-back-next-fed-cut-to-october</link>
      <description><![CDATA[美国就业报告表现强劲，增强了交易员和华尔街经济学家对美联储将推迟进一步降息的预期，导致规模 28 万亿美元的美国国债市场抛售加剧。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-10/treasuries-tumble-as-traders-push-back-next-fed-cut-to-october</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 10 Jan 2025 13:46:56 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>美国药店销售好于预期，沃尔格林股价飙升</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-10/walgreens-posts-stronger-than-expected-revenue-at-us-pharmacies</link>
      <description><![CDATA[沃博联公司 (Walgreens Boots Alliance Inc.) 公布的季度销售额超出了华尔街的预期，推动其股价创下 45 年来的最大涨幅，并缓解了该连锁药店在考虑包括出售在内的战略选择时所面临的压力。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-10/walgreens-posts-stronger-than-expected-revenue-at-us-pharmacies</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 10 Jan 2025 12:00:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>标普 500 指数遭遇“美联储后恐慌”以来最大单日跌幅：市场综述</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-09/stock-market-today-dow-s-p-live-updates</link>
      <description><![CDATA[就业报告公布后，交易员大幅削减对美联储降息的押注，导致股市遭受重创，债券收益率随美元上涨。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-09/stock-market-today-dow-s-p-live-updates</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 09 Jan 2025 22:23:00 GMT</pubDate>
